    "description": "Moxxi weapon. Grants 12 percent lifesteal to all damage dealt while held.\n\nProjectiles explode on impact, dealing splash damage. The explosion deals 80 percent of weapon damage as splash and is increased by grenade damage bonuses.\n\nPlus 15 percent critical hit damage."
