  "notes": "Rubi shots detonate on impact and the splash component is boosted by grenade damage bonuses.\n\nAxton does not receive healing from Sabre Turret damage.\n\nDamaging health bar objects (eg barrels or fuse boxes) will also trigger healing.\n\nSelf damage can still heal you if the hit is fully absorbed by shields; if it reaches health, the lifesteal may partially offset it.",
